<div class="titlepage"><div><div><h3 class="title">
<a name="mysqld-8-0-1-capi"></a>C API Notes</h3></div></div></div>
<div class="itemizedlist"><ul class="itemizedlist" type="disc"><li class="listitem"><p>
        The C API implemented by <code class="literal">libmysqlclient</code> now
        includes a client interface for reading a stream of replication
        events from a MySQL server binary log. For more information, see
        <a class="ulink" href="https://dev.mysql.com/doc/c-api/8.0/en/c-api-binary-log-interface.html" target="_top">C API Binary Log Interface</a>
      </p></li></ul></div>
